          <h1>SMT Inline Cleaning Machine (SMT600 Series)</h1>
          <p class="product-short-desc">
            SMT600 Series — inline SMT cleaning machine with upper and lower adhesive rollers,
            integrated intelligent static elimination, and quick-change window structure for
            fast maintenance and improved SMT production yield.
          </p>

          <div class="product-actions">
            <button class="quote-btn" type="button">Get a Quote</button>
            <a href="https://wa.me/61436605126" target="_blank" class="whatsapp-btn">WhatsApp</a>
          </div>

