      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Product Description</h2>
        <p>
          The SMT Inline Cleaning Machine SMT600 Series is developed for SMT production lines where
          stable surface cleanliness is essential. Upper and lower adhesive rollers clean both sides
          of substrates simultaneously — with no fixed mounting required for flexible, quick operation.
        </p>
        <p>
          The thin cleaning layer prevents deformation or creasing of copper foil and thin film substrates.
          Combined with the integrated intelligent static elimination system and quick-change window
          structure for easy servicing, the SMT600 Series delivers reliable, high-yield cleaning
          in automated electronics manufacturing environments.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="detail-block">
        <h2>Product Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Upper and lower adhesive rollers — no fixed mounting required, flexible and quick to operate</li>
          <li>Thin cleaning layer — does not deform or crease copper foil and thin film substrates</li>
          <li>Special precision adhesive rollers — high efficiency dust and particle removal, improves SMT yield</li>
          <li>Integrated intelligent static elimination system — effectively prevents quality defects caused by static charge</li>
          <li>Adhesive roller shafts and paper roll cartridge with quick-change window structure — easy maintenance and servicing</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

